ESRI GRIDs of bare earth points are also provided. The files were provided in a scheme of FDEM-derived 5,000 x 5,000 foot (1500 x 1500 meter) tiles. Horizontal mapping units are in UTM meters, vertical mapping units are in U.S. survey feet. The total mapping area covers approximately 2102 square miles.</dct:description>         <dcat:keyword>binary</dcat:keyword>         <dcat:keyword>washington county</dcat:keyword>
